# clj-waltawa

AI entry for http://www.ohjelmointiputka.net/kilpa.php?tunnus=valtapeli

## Usage

install leiningen and run with
lein trampoline run

or build a jar and run it with
lein uberjar
java -jar clj-waltawa-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-standalone.jar

## Defensive "algo"
tries to surround the regions occupied by the invader with a zig-zag pattern.
prioritizes biggest regions,
prioritizes moves that are at the center of the map

## Offensive "algo"
tries to expand regions already occupied
prioritizes biggest regions,
prioritizes moves that are at the center of the map

